videos.description: Quentin Grimes rejects an Iowa State shot attempt and at the other end gets a reverse layup to fall.
videos.headline: Grimes blocks shot, finishes and-1 at other end

videos.description: Lindell Wigginton takes advantage of the mismatch and hits a 3-ball for Iowa State.
videos.headline: Wigginton drains deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Lindell Wigginton gets past the Kansas defender and finishes through contact for an Iowa State bucket.
videos.headline: Wigginton blows by defender for lay-in

videos.headline: Weiler-Babb nails 3-pointer
